# ══════════════════════════════════════════
# MODUL 1 — PROFESSOR HUB
# ══════════════════════════════════════════

## Konsepsiya

Professor uchun to'liq "super cockpit" — dars tayyorlashdan boshlab, dars paytida real-time monitoring, kamera orqali diqqat tahlili, va darsdan keyin chuqur analytics.

## 1.1 Metodichka Tizimi

```
PIPELINE:
[Fayl yuklash] → [AI Parsing] → [Tuzilish] → [Dars/Test/Karta] → [Joylashtirish]
   PDF/DOCX         Matn         Mavzular     Avtomatik            Live session
   PPTX/TXT        chiqarish    aniqlash      yaratish
```

## 1.2 KAMERA MONITORING TIZIMI (YANGI, ASOSIY)

### Konsepsiya

Professor dars paytida optik kamera (orqa kamera yoki webcam) orqali butun auditoriyani kuzatadi. AI real-time tahlil qiladi va professorga "sinf harorati" ko'rsatadi.

```
KAMERA PIPELINE:
[Webcam/IP kamera] → [WebRTC stream] → [OpenCV + MediaPipe] → [AI tahlil] → [Dashboard]
                                          Face detection         Diqqat holati    Real-time
                                          Pose estimation        Telefon/gaplash   grafik
                                          Action recognition     Konfuziya
```

## 1.3 Professor Smart Tools

```
CREATIVE TOOLS (Professor Hub da):

1. 🎙️ "Dars Yozuvchisi"
2. 🃏 "Flipped Classroom Generator"
3. 📊 "Qiyinchilik Xaritasi"
4. 🎯 "Maqsad Tracker"
5. 📅 "Smart Calendar"
6. 🤖 "AI Ko'mak"
7. 📝 "Instant Rubric"
8. 🎬 "Presentation Enhancer"
9. 📱 "QR Homework"
10. 🏆 "Class Competition"
```

