# ══════════════════════════════════════════
# MODUL 3 — STUDENT HUB (Shaxsiy O'quv Markazi)
# ══════════════════════════════════════════

## Konsepsiya

O'quvchi uchun **shaxsiy AI o'quv yo'ldoshi** — nafaqat test yechish, balki o'z bilimini oshirish, zaif tomonlarini topish, va maqsadga erishish uchun to'liq ekosistema.

```
STUDENT HUB TIZIMI:

📊 DASHBOARD        🧠 AI MENTOR        📚 KUTUBXONA
Kunlik vazifalar    Savol-javob         Barcha fanlar
Streak tracker      Tushuntirish        Konspektlar
XP va levellar      Plan tuzish         Videolar

🃏 FLASHCARDS       👥 PEER ZONE        🎯 GOALS
Spaced repetition   Do'stlar            Maqsad qo'yish
SM-2 algoritm       Guruhllar           Progress kuzatish
Emoji feedback      Savol-javob forum   Milestone tizimi
```

## 3.1 Creative Student Hub Features

```
1. 🗺️ "BILIM XARITASI" (Knowledge Map)
2. 🤖 "SHAXSIY AI USTOZ"
3. 🎯 "MICRO-GOALS TIZIMI"
4. 📱 "SNAP & LEARN" (Kamera bilan o'qish)
5. 🔮 "IMTIHON BASHORATI"
6. 🎙️ "OVOZLI JAVOB"
7. 🏅 "ACHIEVEMENT TIZIMI"
8. 👥 "PEER LEARNING ZONE"
9. 📅 "SMART STUDY PLANNER"
10. 🌊 "FLOW STATE TRACKER"
11. 🎮 "DAILY QUEST"
12. 🔄 "SPACED REPETITION ENGINE" (SM-2)
```

